ary">Fachinformatiker Anwendungsentwicklung<span class="modern-minimal__entry-company"> · BBQ Düsseldorf</span></div><div class="modern-minimal__entry-date">Aug. 2024 – Juli 2026</div></div></div></section><section class="modern-minimal__section"><h2 class="modern-minimal__section-heading">Kenntnisse</h2><div class="modern-minimal__skills-grid"><div class="modern-minimal__skills-group"><span class="modern-minimal__skills-label">Backend</span><span class="modern-minimal__skills-items">Node.js, Prisma</span></div><div class="modern-minimal__skills-group"><span class="modern-minimal__skills-label">Frontend</span><span class="modern-minimal__skills-items">React, Tailwind</span></div></div></section><section class="modern-minimal__section"><h2 class="modern-minimal__section-heading">Sprachen</h2><div class="modern-minimal__languages"><span class="modern-minimal__language-item">Deutsch<span class="modern-minimal__language-level"> — native</span></span><span class="modern-minimal__language-item">Englisch<span class="modern-minimal__language-level"> — B2</span></span></div></section><section class="modern-minimal__section"><h2 class="modern-minimal__section-heading">Projekte</h2><div class="modern-minimal__entry"><div class="modern-minimal__entry-head"><div class="modern-minimal__entry-primary">FlashBuddy</div></div><div class="modern-minimal__entry-location">SaaS</div><p class="modern-minimal__summary" style="margin-top:4pt">Lern-Karten App.</p></div></section></div></article>"`;
